data.chText: （大学）一年级新生；（中学）九年级学生
data.enText: a student who is in his or her first year at a university or college, or in the ninth grade at school

data.chText: 高中 / 大学一年级新生

data.enText: a first-year student at a university or college

tr: any new participant in some activity
used of a person in the first year of an experience (especially in United States high school or college)
example: freshman year in high school or college

value.def: In America, a freshman is a student who is in his or her first year at university or college.
